  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, ginger, and garlic. Cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add curry powder, cumin powder, and garam masala. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add paneer cheese and cook until it starts to brown.",
    "Pour in heavy cream and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and let the curry simmer for 10-15 minutes.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot over basmati rice or with naan bread.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro or scallions, if desired.",
